name: Gain six Abs
details: Everyone has abdominal muscles, or “abs.” For well-defined abs, most people will need to lose some body fat around the stomach and then build muscle. Both males and females can achieve well-defined abs, but genetic and hormonal factors can make it more challenging for females.
